# Markdown Formatting Rules

- **ALWAYS adhere to markdownlint rules** - Run markdownlint on all markdown files
- **NEVER use bold on markdown headings** - `## Heading` NOT `## **Heading**`
- **ALWAYS add blank lines between sections** - One blank line before and after each heading
- **Use proper markdown syntax** - No invalid characters or formatting
- **Keep headings clean** - Just `## Heading` without any extra formatting
- **Use consistent spacing** - One blank line between sections, no extra spaces
- **No trailing whitespace** - Clean line endings
